properties.flavorText: A reprogrammed Clockborg fitted with additional arrow launching devices.
A reprogrammed Clockborg left behind to maintain the complex mechanisms running the Deep Well.
Left broken and contorted by whatever horrible creature is making that ghastly sound echoing from below.
The remains of a powerful adventurer left contorted and dead by whatever horrible creature lives at the base of the Deep Well.
Use caution when accessing the base of the Deep Well!
A simple wooden bucket reinforced with iron bands. Attached to a length of rope that has been severed.
Too heavy to be of much use.
Area still under construction. Mind the gap!
A pristine part from the Deep Well mechanisms.
There is an image of a glowing figure standing atop a mountain.
A waterproof chest that may only be unlocked by experienced swimmers and divers.
